'''房利美'''（'''Fannie Mae'''，{{Otcbb|FNMA}}，旧名'''联邦国民抵押贷款协会'''），是美國最大的[[美国|美国]]特許企業。主要业务是在美国房屋[[抵押贷款|抵押贷款]]的[[二级市场|二级市场]]中收购贷款，并通过向投资者发行机构[[债券|债券]]或[[证券化|证券化]]的[[抵押债券|抵押债券]]，以较低成本集资，赚取[[利差|利差]]。

==政府接管==
在[[次贷危机|次贷危机]]持续，房贷市场低迷、[[法拍屋|法拍屋]]大幅增加的情况下，美国政府于2008年9月7日宣布以高达2000亿美元的可能代价，接管了濒临[[破产|破产]]的房利美及另一家政府赞助企业[[房地美|房地美]]<ref name='Bloomberg-CBO-2008-09-11'>{{cite news | last = Kopecki | first = Dawn | work = [[彭博通訊社|彭博通訊社]] | date = 2008-09-11 | accessdate = 2008-09-11 | url = http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601109&sid=adr.czwVm3ws&refer=home | title = U.S. Considers Bringing Fannie, Freddie on to Budget | archive-date = 2018-12-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181225174557/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=ef2ffae0-086c-11e9-93fa-35b20649c9c0&url=L2FwcHMvbmV3cz9waWQ9MjA2MDExMDkmc2lkPWFkci5jendWbTN3cyZyZWZlcj1ob21lJTIw | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name='Economist-Suffering Seizure-2008-09-08 '>{{cite news | first =  | last =  | coauthors =  | title = Suffering a seizure: America's government takes control of Freddie Mac and Fannie Mae | date = 2008-09-08 | publisher = [[经济学人|经济学人]] | url = http://www.economist.com/finance/displaystory.cfm?story_id=12078933 | work = Economist.com | pages =  | accessdate = 2008-09-11 | archive-date = 2008-09-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080913213436/http://www.economist.com/finance/displayStory.cfm?story_id=12078933 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[美国政府|美国政府]]中对房利美的原直接监管单位为[[联邦住屋企业督察局|联邦住屋企业督察局]]（OFHEO, Office of Federal Housing Enterprise Oversight），现为新成立的[[联邦住房金融局|联邦住房金融局]]（Federal Housing Finance Agency）。

